 *   `CombatSystem` alongside `ObjectUpdateSystem`.
 * - @ref tutorial_ai_behavior — Attach an AI brain and behavior
 *   tree to your NPCs.
 * - `advanced/ECS_DEEP_DIVE.md` — Internal data structures,
 *   parallelism, and the scheduler's dependency graph.
 * - `include/cgs/game/components.hpp` — authoritative source for
 *   the four core components.
 */
